data.description: Step into this meticulously maintained 1.5-story (1 owner) corner lot home, that reflects care and pride of ownership! This charming layout offers 3BD, 4BA and 2 car garage. Appreciate the large entry way followed by a front room, perfect for creating a cozy sitting area. Enjoy your roomy eat-in kitchen with a spacious island that has ample counter space, (appliances included) and has a formal dining room! Main level primary bedroom is complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring a shower and jetted tub! A generously sized walk-in closet provides ample storage space for your wardrobe. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms with a jack and jill bathroom. The basement adds valuable living space to this already impressive home, featuring a large rec area and fourth non-conforming room. There is an additional extra space that is perfect for a playroom or hobby/craft room! Step outside to the fenced backyard where an overhang provides shade and shelter for outdoor activities.
